{"data":[{"date":"16:09 25/06","title":"HAGL m\u1ea5t V\u0103n Thanh tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/9/24/hagl-mat-van-thanh-truoc-tran-tai-dau-than-quang-ninh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 16 V-League, CLB HAGL s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh V\u0169 V\u0103n Thanh do \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2 v\u00ec th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HAGL m\u1ea5t V\u0103n Thanh v\u00ec th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 V\u0169 V\u0103n Thanh \u0111\u00e3 l\u0129nh \u0111\u1ee7 3 t\u1ea5m th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c anh s\u1ebd v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a VFF.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HAGL m\u1ea5t V\u0169 V\u0103n Thanh tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HAGL m\u1ea5t V\u0169 V\u0103n Thanh tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/9/24/HAGL-tiet-lo-doi-bong-nuoc-ngoai-muon-co-Van-Thanh-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 V\u0169 V\u0103n Thanh kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16 v\u00ec \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2. \u1ea2nh: Zing.vn</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf v\u1edbi HAGL khi m\u00e0 V\u0103n Thanh lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf n\u01a1i h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a HAGL. S\u1ef1 \u0111a n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 qu\u00ea H\u1ea3i D\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m t\u1ed1t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u1edf hai c\u00e1nh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nh\u00f4 cao \u0111\u00e1 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c V\u0103n Thanh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh s\u1ebd b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed Nguy\u1ec5n Phong H\u1ed3ng Duy \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00e1m v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y. C\u00e1nh c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Nguy\u1ec5n H\u1eefu Anh T\u00e0i, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a V\u0103n Thanh, CLB HAGL c\u0169ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7 V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh \u2013 T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn do \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t ngu\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a VFF. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u201cG\u1ed7\u201d s\u1ebd th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m trung v\u1ec7 ngo\u1ea1i binh m\u1edbi m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111ang t\u00ednh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng cho giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u1ede ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng M\u1ecf c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7\u00a0\u0110\u00e0o Nh\u1eadt Minh v\u00ec l\u00fd do t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. V\u0103n Thanh, Nh\u1eadt Minh l\u00e0 hai trong s\u1ed1 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 16 do \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ee7 3 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa HAGL vs Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 18h00 ng\u00e0y mai 26/6. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, HAGL \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-3 t\u1ea1i C\u1ea9m Ph\u1ea3 tuy nhi\u00ean khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai th\u01b0\u1eddng thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a l\u00e2u.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3815","checkdouble":"189518"},{"date":"16:35 25/06","title":"U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/u19-viet-nam-ton-that-nhan-su-truoc-them-giai-u19-dong-nam-a.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1 2018, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn ca ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng Ti\u1ebfn Anh sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u Evergrande.</h2><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng Ti\u1ebfn Anh b\u1ecb g\u00e3y tay tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1ea5t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng Ti\u1ebfn Anh  tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1ea5t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng Ti\u1ebfn Anh  tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/tien-anh-0007.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng Ti\u1ebfn Anh l\u1ee1 h\u1eb9n v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1 2018 v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh B c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u Evergrande, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn tin d\u1eef khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 vai tr\u00f2 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng Ti\u1ebfn Anh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng may b\u1ecb g\u00e3y tay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau m\u1ed9t pha va ch\u1ea1m v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u Evergrande B, Ti\u1ebfn Anh \u0111\u00e3 ng\u00e3 \u1edf t\u01b0 th\u1ebf b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9ng khi\u1ebfn anh ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ed1ng tay ph\u1ea3i xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n v\u00e0 b\u1ecb \u0111au. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 ch\u1ee5p phim cho th\u1ea5y Ti\u1ebfn Anh b\u1ecb g\u00e3y x\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00e1nh tay v\u00e0 bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n Ti\u1ebfn Anh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, khi m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 tu\u1ea7n n\u1eefa l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 s\u1ebd kh\u1edfi tranh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch, ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (25/6) th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n s\u1ebd tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n. Ri\u00eang Ti\u1ebfn Anh s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00e1n b\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a VFF \u1edf l\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c th\u00eam \u00edt ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n ca ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o VFF sau khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb, \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean Ti\u1ebfn Anh c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1eadp trung \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1edbm b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c. V\u1edbi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1eeba g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i, Ti\u1ebfn Anh \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Indonesia trong v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: robotoslab-regular, serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3814","checkdouble":"189523"},{"date":"16:53 25/06","title":"HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0103n may, kh\u00f3 \u0111i s\u00e2u","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/25/hlv-le-thuy-hai-nhan-dinh-dt-nhat-ban-an-may-kho-di-sau.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i cho r\u1eb1ng \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng may v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ph\u00f9 tang kh\u00f3 \u0111i s\u00e2u.</h2><h2>HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n th\u1eafng may</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia nh\u1edd \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i 1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ngay \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 1. Sang t\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai, \u2018c\u00e1c Samurai xanh\u2019 ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 2-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Senegal ch\u01a1i \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u01b0ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Le Thuy Hai tu tin co the lam tot vi tri GDKT o doi tuyen Viet Nam\" title=\"HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed G\u0110KT \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2015/10/22/hlv-hai-lo-toi-tu-tin-co-the-lam-tot-gdkt-o-doi-tuyen.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i xa t\u1ea1i World Cup c\u1ee7a \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i t\u00e2m s\u1ef1 tr\u00ean Vietnamnet: \u201cTh\u1ef1c ra b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec gh\u00ea g\u1edbm c\u1ea3.\u00a0\u1ede\u00a0tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, Colombia m\u1ea5t ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1edbm v\u00e0 l\u1ea1i thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i trong hi\u1ec7p 2 n\u00ean Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.Tr\u1eadn h\u00f4m qua Nh\u1eadt c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u01a1n g\u00ec\u00a0Senegal, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed may m\u1eafn g\u1ee1\u00a0h\u00f2a v\u00e0 c\u1ed1\u00a0gi\u1eef\u00a0k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3\u00a0\u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3\u00a0c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00e2n t\u00edch k\u1ef9 h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, \u00f4ng H\u1ea3i \u2018l\u01a1\u2019 cho bi\u1ebft th\u00eam: \u201c\u0110\u00e1ng l\u1ebd\u00a0Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u1ea7n ch\u01a1i ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p nhanh, nh\u1ecf, ban b\u1eadt \u0111\u1ec3\u00a0ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p h\u01a1n v\u1edbi th\u1ec3\u00a0h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 th\u1ec3\u00a0l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Hai tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua h\u1ecd\u00a0kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3\u00a0hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec r\u00f5 n\u00e9t. T\u00f4i xin nh\u1eafc l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng trong th\u00ec c\u0169ng l\u00e0 do may m\u1eafn b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7\u00a0t\u1ef1\u00a0thua, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp th\u00ec c\u0169ng th\u1ebf\u00a0th\u00f4i, kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd\u00a0\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1eefa \u0111\u00e2u\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb c\u1ef1u G\u0110KT Becamex B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cB\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00ec v\u1ee9t, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 World Cup. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9\u00a0khen Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ea3\u00a0c\u1ea3m, chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng t\u1ed1t th\u00f4i, nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c ra \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0o t\u1edbi World Cup ch\u1eb3ng v\u1eady.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0\u00a0Panama h\u1ecd\u00a0thua \u0111\u1eadm nh\u01b0\u00a0th\u1ebf\u00a0nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec3\u00a0c\u00f3 b\u00e0n danh d\u1ef1. Ba Lan c\u0169ng v\u1eady, h\u1ecd\u00a0b\u1ecb\u00a0lo\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd\u00a0bu\u00f4ng xu\u00f4i c\u1ea3. H\u00e3y c\u1ee9\u00a0xem tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u01b0\u00a0n\u00e0o v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n\u201d, HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i chia s\u1ebb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n l\u00e3o l\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam hy v\u1ecdng \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n cho ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp song \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i s\u00e2u t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Akira Nishino b\u1edfi t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup</span> c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 chung kh\u00e1t khao chinh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cuc-dien-bang-h-truoc-luot-tran-cuoi-cho-doi-nhung-bat-ngo-421-189462.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/cuc-dien-bang-h-truoc-luot-tran-cuoi-cho-doi-nhung-bat-ngo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cuc-dien-bang-h-truoc-luot-tran-cuoi-cho-doi-nhung-bat-ngo-421-189462.html\">C\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n b\u1ea3ng H tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i: \u0110i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp?</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Colombia gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ba Lan, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam M\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. V\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/dt-nhat-ban-sang-cua-di-tiep-dung-coi-thuong-nhung-chang-lun-466-189471.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/dt-nhat-ban-sang-cua-di-tiep-dung-coi-thuong-nhung-chang-lun.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/dt-nhat-ban-sang-cua-di-tiep-dung-coi-thuong-nhung-chang-lun-466-189471.html\">\u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n: \u0110\u1eebng coi th\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u1eefng ch\u00e0ng l\u00f9n</span><br>\r\nNh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng khi HLV Akira Nishino ki\u00ean tr\u00ec v\u1edbi con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hoa-qua-cam-cua-dt-nhat-ban-truoc-senegal-421-189460.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/Du-am-Nhat-Ban-2-2-Senegal-Tinh-than-Samurai-va-niem-hy-vong-chau-A-hinh-anh-3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hoa-qua-cam-cua-dt-nhat-ban-truoc-senegal-421-189460.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Senegal</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Senegal, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec3 hai l\u1ea7n san h\u00f2a c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3813","checkdouble":"189526"},{"date":"15:39 25/06","title":"Barca v\u00e0 Real \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao Bayern Munich","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/barca-va-real-dai-chien-vi-sao-bayern-munich.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real v\u00e0 Barca \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Thiago Alcantara r\u1eddi Bayern Munich, c\u1ea3 hai g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 60 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real v\u00e0 Barca h\u1ecfi mua Thiago Alcantara</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Thiago Alcantara ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Bayern Munich. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ra s\u00e2n 32 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng, ghi 7 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 2 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real v\u00e0 Barca mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Thiago Alcantara r\u1eddi Bayern Munich h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real v\u00e0 Barca mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Thiago Alcantara r\u1eddi Bayern Munich h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/barca-va-real-dai-chien-vi-sao-bayern-munich.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real v\u00e0 Barca quan t\u00e2m Thiago Alcantara</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh T\u00e2y Ban Nha tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 gi\u00fap anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal v\u00e0 Barca \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Thiago Alcantara r\u1eddi Bayern Munich \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018. Los Blancos \u0111ang nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i nh\u1eb1m thay th\u1ebf cho Mateo Kovacic, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Julen Lopetegui \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-nham-nguoi-cu-barca-nang-cap-tuyen-giua-180-189259.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real mua Thiago</span>. Barca c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha nh\u1eb1m thay th\u1ebf s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Iniesta.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nThiago \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Barca t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2009 \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2013, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Barca.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Bayern ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n Thiago v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u euro</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo t\u1edd Sport c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Real v\u00e0 Barca ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 60 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Bayern Munich b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u1edd Bild c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c th\u00ec kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d s\u1ebd nh\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 70 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thiago Alcantara dinh chan thuong nghiem trong\" title=\"Thiago Alcantara d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/23/real-madrid-nham-nguoi-cu-barca-nang-cap-tuyen-giua.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bayern mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 70 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u1eeb Thiago Alcantara\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Real v\u00e0 Barca chi ra ch\u1ec9 k\u00e9m kho\u1ea3n ph\u00ed m\u00e0 Bayern \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi c\u00f3 10 tri\u1ec7u euro, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng m\u1ed9t trong hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1ee7 70 tri\u1ec7u euro nh\u01b0 ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn gi\u00e0nh Thiago gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a TBN \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t, v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3812","checkdouble":"189512"},{"date":"15:56 25/06","title":"Bayern t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i trao \u0111\u1ed5i sao kh\u1ee7ng v\u1edbi Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/bayern-tu-choi-trao-doi-sao-khung-voi-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Robert Lewandowski, h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng d\u00f9ng ti\u1ec1n c\u1ed9ng Karim Benzema \u0111\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Bayern \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i trao \u0111\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1edbi Los Blancos.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng d\u00f9ng Benzema c\u00e2u Lewandowski</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Real Madrid, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed T\u00e2y Ban Nha, c\u1ef1u HLV c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n TBN mu\u1ed1n t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1edbn tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Robert Lewandowski thay Karim Benzema h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Robert Lewandowski thay Karim Benzema h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/5/Real-Madrid-muon-mua-Robert-Lewandowski-thay-Karim-Benzema-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Lewandowski</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKarim Benzema \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, HLV Lopetegui mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea9y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ra \u0111i v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha nh\u1eafm Robert Lewandowski nh\u01b0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t th\u00edch phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ba Lan, trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y Real \u0111\u1ec1u quan t\u00e2m Lewandowski song kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u00f4ng Lopetegui ch\u1ea5m Lewandowski, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Real s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Bayern kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, b\u1edfi v\u1eady K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u00f3 c\u01b0\u1ee1ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-bo-kane-mua-lewandowski-trong-mua-he-toi-180-182572.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Robert Lewandowski</span>, h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng d\u00f9ng ti\u1ec1n c\u1ed9ng Karim Benzema \u0111\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Bayern t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i trao \u0111\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1edbi Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng d\u00f9ng 40 tri\u1ec7u euro c\u1ed9ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Karim Benzema \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Bayern nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, song \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bayern tu choi trao doi giua Lewandowski va Benzema\" title=\"Bayern t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i trao \u0111\u1ed5i gi\u1eefa Lewandowski v\u00e0 Benzema\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/bayern-tu-choi-trao-doi-sao-khung-voi-real-madrid.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bayern t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i trao \u0111\u1ed5i gi\u1eefa Lewandowski v\u00e0 Benzema</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKicker tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 Bayern s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ba Lan v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef Lewandowski \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin cho r\u1eb1ng Lewandowski mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Bayern sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y, song v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c, nh\u1eefng CLB mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ba Lan s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Real th\u00ec Chelsea c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Lewandowski, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ph\u00eda Bayern v\u1eabn c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3811","checkdouble":"189513"},{"date":"17:58 25/06","title":"Juventus chi 20 tri\u1ec7u Euro s\u0103n tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Atletico","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/25/juventus-mua-godin-gia-20-trieu-euro.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Godin gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u Euro. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia tin r\u1eb1ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid song \u0111\u00e3 32 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Atletico kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Godin</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDiego Godin gia nh\u1eadp Atletico Madrid n\u0103m 2010 t\u1eeb Villarreal. Trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay d\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ni\u1ec1m tin t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m qua. C\u00f9ng nhau, h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh 7 danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn nh\u1ecf b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111i t\u1edbi chung k\u1ebft Champions League 2 n\u0103m 2014 v\u00e0 2016.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGodin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1eabu h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 hi\u1ebfm hoi c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Ngo\u00e0i kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng, \u1edf c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f2n to\u00e1t ra phong th\u00e1i th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh. Th\u00eam n\u1eefa, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a anh c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. Trong 8 m\u00f9a \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i cho Atletico, trung b\u00ecnh m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a Godin c\u00f3 g\u1ea7n 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. C\u00e1 bi\u1ec7t c\u00f3 m\u00f9a 2013/14, anh \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 8 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Godin gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u Euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Godin gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u Euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/juventus-mua-godin-gia-20-trieu-euro.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Godin ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Atletico</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Godin \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 32. V\u00e0 d\u00f9 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Uruguay ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, ph\u00eda Atletico c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n. H\u1ecd c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng Jose Gimenez, Stefan Savic, Lucas Hernandez tr\u1ebb trung h\u01a1n v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng m\u1eb7n m\u00e0 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Godin.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Atletico</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin tr\u00ean, Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Godin gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u Euro. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, trung v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1986 v\u1eabn cho th\u1ea5y phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 Atletico mu\u1ed1n h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn d\u00e0i h\u01a1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Godin phat bieu ve Salah\" title=\"Godin ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Salah\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/diego-godin-ai-cap-co-salah-hay-khong-cung-vay-thoi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Godin gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u Euro</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f2n Juventus th\u00ec kh\u00e1c. Sau khi bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 Leonardo Bonucci ra \u0111i, \u201cB\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0\u201d thi\u1ebfu \u0111i m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u00fac chuy\u1ec3n sang \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi 3 trung v\u1ec7. T\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Beppe Marotta hi\u1ec7n mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh m\u1edbi cho h\u1eadu ph\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi Godin, \u01b0u ti\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00e0 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico. Tuy nhi\u00ean, anh \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ecf m\u1ecdi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng x\u1ea3y ra. B\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juventus c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec9nh cao v\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 32 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1edbt l\u1edd. C\u00f2n Atletico, \u0111\u1ec3 Godin ra \u0111i v\u00e0 thu v\u1ec1 20 tri\u1ec7u Euro ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 s\u1ebd t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd m\u1ea5t tr\u1eafng anh sau \u0111\u00e2y 1 n\u0103m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Juventus tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/juventus-ra-gia-pjanic-it-nhat-80-trieu-euro-176-189062.html\">Juventus b\u00e1o gi\u00e1 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t cho Real v\u00e0 Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-nhan-don-dau-vu-sao-juventus-172-188630.html\">Chelsea nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f2n \u0111au v\u1ee5 sao Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/cska-tu-choi-ban-golovin-cho-juventus-176-188909.html\">CSKA t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng World Cup cho \u0111\u1ea1i gia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-tu-choi-mua-sao-khung-juventus-voi-gia-53-trieu-bang-172-188375.html\">MU t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i mua sao kh\u1ee7ng Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3810","checkdouble":"189533"},{"date":"15:16 25/06","title":"Fellaini l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/7/fellaini-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Marouane Fellaini ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh s\u1ebd s\u1edbm c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 vi\u1ec7c \u0111i hay \u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Fellaini s\u1eafp h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi M.U</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMarouane Fellaini c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn M.U \u1edf H\u00e8 2013 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 27.5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb Everton. Trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt, anh ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00f2n vai. Nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Fellaini ch\u01a1i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Marouane Fellaini ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Marouane Fellaini ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/5/Marouane-Fellaini-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Fellaini h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi MU v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7 t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Fellaini \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 y\u00eau th\u00edch phong c\u00e1ch v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n M.U gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n ng\u00f4i sao 31 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Fellaini v\u1edbi M.U s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 01/07 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y anh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Old Trafford theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do. M.U \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n nh\u01b0ng Fellaini \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/ac-milan-xac-nhan-chuan-bi-co-fellaini-172-186816.html\" target=\"_blank\">AC Milan \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Fellaini</span>, Juventus hay PSG c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i. \u1ede Anh, Arsenal, Everton v\u00e0 West Ham l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i\u00a0b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Fellaini l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Marouane Fellaini ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh s\u1ebd s\u1edbm c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 vi\u1ec7c \u0111i hay \u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fellaini van chung to duoc gia tri cua minh\" title=\"Fellaini v\u1eabn ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/30/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-hom-nay-ngay-96-tin-nong-chuyen-nhuong-he-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Fellaini s\u1ebd s\u1edbm quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cB\u1ea1n s\u1ebd bi\u1ebft s\u1edbm th\u00f4i, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 suy ngh\u0129 r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn s\u1eb5n th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 vi\u1ec7c \u0111i hay \u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd s\u1edbm c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Fellaini s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7 n\u00e0y, hi\u1ec7n anh \u0111ang c\u00f9ng \u0110T B\u1ec9 tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 \u1edf Nga.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Fellaini ra \u0111i, M.U c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i qu\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng. Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Fred t\u1eeb Shakhtar Donetsk, \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi\u00a0Brazil Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i chi 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Fred r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi M.U nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Michael Carrick \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 c\u00f2n Fellaini v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3809","checkdouble":"189509"},{"date":"16:34 25/06","title":"Dortmund l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ee5 quan t\u00e2m Morata","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/9/dortmund-len-tieng-vu-quan-tam-morata.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Dortmund mua Alvaro Morata kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Michael Zorc c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Ruhr x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dortmund \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n quan t\u00e2m Morata</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 v\u1eeba qua Dortmund \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Aubameyang cho Arsenal v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, vi\u1ec7c Michy Batshuayi m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb Chelsea \u0111ang ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Gabon.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Dortmund mua Alvaro Morata kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Dortmund mua Alvaro Morata kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/22/Kha-nang-Dortmund-mua-Alvaro-Morata-khong-the-xay-ra-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Dortmund \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n quan t\u00e2m Morata</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nDortmund d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh mua \u0111\u1ee9t Michy Batshuayi v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Chelsea kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Ruhr.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Roman Abramovich \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u00eam cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao khi m\u01b0\u1ee3n Batshuayi, Dortmund kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 k\u00e8m theo \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nG\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 trong vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Batshuayi, Dortmund h\u1ecfi mua Morata. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o The Blues, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng nh\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Dortmund s\u1edf h\u1eefu Morata l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 s\u00e1ng n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 chi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Chelsea y\u00eau c\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Dortmund t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i mua Morata v\u00ec gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Dortmund mua Alvaro Morata kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Michael Zorc c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Ruhr x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Dortmund mua Alvaro Morata kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Dortmund mua Alvaro Morata kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/9/dortmund-len-tieng-vu-quan-tam-morata.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Dortmund ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c quan t\u00e2m Morata</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cKh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i quan t\u00e2m Morata, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chi 58 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0 ph\u00eda Chelsea \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi. Dortmund c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 ti\u1ec1m l\u1ef1c t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 Morata \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00fang l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n mua m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o m\u1edbi, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng chi ra m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn. T\u00e0i ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Dortmund c\u00f3 h\u1ea1n v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1eeba s\u1ee9c v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1m l\u1ef1c t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a CLB\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDortmund \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat lui trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Morata, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u00fac n\u00e0y thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Juventus v\u00e0 PSG. PSG s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng nh\u1ea3 Cavani \u0111\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ef1u sao Real, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/juventus-chi-60-trieu-euro-mua-sao-khung-chelsea-172-185574.html\" target=\"_blank\">Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Morata</span>, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 60 tri\u1ec7u euro cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3808","checkdouble":"189514"},{"date":"16:51 25/06","title":"M.U c\u00f3 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n B ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1ee5 Milinkovic-Savic","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/1/mu-co-phuong-an-b-chat-luong-vu-milinkovicsavic.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU mu\u1ed1n mua Lorenzo Pellegrini c\u1ee7a Roma trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Sergej Milinkovic-Savic c\u1ee7a Lazio \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro cho Milinkovic-Savic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed nh\u1eafc r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c MU quan t\u00e2m Milinkovic-Savic c\u1ee7a Lazio. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia, anh ghi t\u1edbi 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Serie A m\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU mu\u1ed1n mua Lorenzo Pellegrini c\u1ee7a Roma thay Milinkovic-Savic  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU mu\u1ed1n mua Lorenzo Pellegrini c\u1ee7a Roma thay Milinkovic-Savic  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/MU-muon-mua-Lorenzo-Pellegrini-cua-Roma-thay-Milinkovic-Savic--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Milinkovic-Savic\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSergej Milinkovic-Savic l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m to\u00e0n n\u0103ng, anh c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng, ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o hay d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t. Mourinho nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf cho Carrick.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, M.U ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n. Ph\u00eda Lazio li\u00ean t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m kh\u00f3 M.U trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn quan t\u00e2m l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Lazio h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 c\u1ef1c cao cho Milinkovic-Savic.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Manchester Evening News, M.U s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng chi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Lazio y\u00eau c\u1ea7u, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra t\u1ed1i \u0111a 80 tri\u1ec7u euro m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n h\u1ecd s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 kh\u00e1c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>MU c\u00f3 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n B v\u1ee5 Milinkovic-Savic</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU mu\u1ed1n mua Lorenzo Pellegrini c\u1ee7a Roma trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Sergej Milinkovic-Savic c\u1ee7a Lazio \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Lorenzo Pellegrini\" title=\"tien ve Lorenzo Pellegrini\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/1/mu-co-phuong-an-b-chat-luong-vu-milinkovicsavic.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Lorenzo Pellegrini trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Milinkovic-Savic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua Pellegrini ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Roma, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u0111a n\u0103ng khi v\u1eeba h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t l\u1ea1i v\u1eeba c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua anh ghi 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 4 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o sau 22 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf Serie A.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPellegrini gia nh\u1eadp Roma m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 10 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u1eeb Sassuolo, M.U \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 30 tri\u1ec7u euro s\u1ebd thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i MU th\u00ec <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/arsenal-muon-vuot-mat-mu-vu-sao-roma-172-187019.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Pellegrini</span>, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 30 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 v\u00e9 tham d\u1ef1 Champions League l\u00e0 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap M.U c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n Arsenal trong vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3807","checkdouble":"189517"},{"date":"09:21 25/06","title":"\u0110\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Barca vs Real v\u00ec sao tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/25/barca-va-real-muon-mua-thiago-alcantara.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barca v\u00e0 Real mu\u1ed1n mua Thiago Alcantara, hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Bayern Munich. M\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n y\u00eau c\u1ea7u n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha ra \u0111i l\u00ean t\u1edbi 70 tri\u1ec7u Euro.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Barca mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Thiago</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nThiago Alcantara t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb Barcelona trong v\u00f2ng 6 n\u0103m (2005 t\u1edbi 2011). D\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Pep Guardiola, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00f4n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i 1 v\u00e0 g\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou mu\u1ed1n anh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi k\u1ebf t\u1ee5c cho c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n Xavi v\u00e0 Andres Iniesta.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Thiago kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edbi ng\u00e0y \u1ea5y. Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi hai bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00f3i tr\u00ean c\u1ee7a Barca, anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1ch ra \u0111i. \u0110\u1ea7u m\u00f9a 2013/14, Thiago \u0111i theo ti\u1ebfng g\u1ecdi c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y c\u0169 Guardiola t\u1ea1i Bayern Munich.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca v\u00e0 Real mu\u1ed1n mua Thiago Alcantara, hi\u1ec7n ch\u01a1i cho Bayern h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Barca v\u00e0 Real mu\u1ed1n mua Thiago Alcantara, hi\u1ec7n ch\u01a1i cho Bayern h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/barca-va-real-muon-mua-thiago-alcantara.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Barca mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 Thiago Alcantara</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng m\u00f9a 2014/15, qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian v\u1eeba qua ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Thiago h\u1ed3i sinh trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0110\u1ee9c. Qua \u0111\u00f3, anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i gia bao g\u1ed3m ch\u00ednh CLB th\u1eddi ni\u00ean thi\u1ebfu Barcelona. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nG\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 x\u1ee9 Catalonia m\u1edbi chia tay Iniesta (sang Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n) v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf. Nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd nh\u01b0 Andre Gomes hay Denis Suarez kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi HLV Ernesto Valverde.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>El Clasico v\u00ec tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 TBN</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin m\u00e0 t\u1edd Sport \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, Barca v\u00e0 Real mu\u1ed1n mua Thiago Alcantara. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, Barca d\u00f9 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c h\u1ed9i ng\u1ed9 v\u1edbi Thiago nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. Real c\u00f3 v\u0169 kh\u00ed l\u00e0 HLV Julen Lopetegui trong tay. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 51 tu\u1ed5i m\u1edbi nh\u1eadm ch\u1ee9c thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Los Blancos thay Zinedine Zidane n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay sau m\u00f9a 2017/18.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thiago Alcantara dinh chan thuong nghiem trong\" title=\"Thiago Alcantara d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/23/real-madrid-nham-nguoi-cu-barca-nang-cap-tuyen-giua.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Barca v\u00e0 Real mu\u1ed1n mua Thiago Alcantara</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Guardiola, Lopetegui l\u00e0 HLV c\u00f3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Thiago. H\u1ecd c\u00f9ng nhau g\u1eafn b\u00f3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i U19 t\u1edbi U21 T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh c\u00e1c ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t n\u0103m 2012 v\u00e0 2013. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Thiago, Real coi nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 tri\u1ec7t ti\u00eau s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Bayern Munich s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 Thiago ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 70 tri\u1ec7u Euro. M\u1ed9t con s\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 nh\u1ecf v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta ch\u1edd xem Real v\u00e0 Barca ai s\u1ebd b\u1ea1o tay h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/barca-real-va-psg-dai-chien-vi-sao-chelsea-172-189414.html\">Barca, Real v\u00e0 PSG \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/sao-man-city-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-barca-180-189345.html\">Sao Man City c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nham-sao-barca-nang-cap-hang-thu-172-189276.html\">MU nh\u1eafm sao Barca n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-muon-mua-sao-mu-sau-su-ra-di-cua-iniesta-180-189268.html\">Barca mu\u1ed1n mua sao M.U sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Iniesta</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3806","checkdouble":"189489"},{"date":"09:46 25/06","title":"M.U c\u1eed \u0111i\u1ec7p vi\u00ean th\u0103m d\u00f2 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i sao s\u00e1ng Serbia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/mu-muon-mua-milinkovicsavic-va-dung-chieu-doc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M.U d\u00f9ng Matic th\u0103m d\u00f2 Milinkovic-Savic. H\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n th\u00f4ng qua tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 21 tu\u1ed5i trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM.U mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Milinkovic-Savic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSergej Milinkovic-Savic \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f3n h\u00e0ng \u201chot\u201d tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Trong 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Lazio. Nh\u01b0 m\u00f9a 2017/18 ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n, kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i, Milinkovic-Savic c\u00f2n tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ghi 12 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o 3 l\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f9ng \u0110T Serbia d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018, Milinkovic-Savic ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng. Ch\u01a1i ph\u00eda sau ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1eafm Aleksandar Mitrovic, anh ph\u00e1t huy h\u1ebft t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u1eeb pressing b\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn hay ki\u1ebfn thi\u1ebft, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU d\u00f9ng Matic th\u0103m d\u00f2 Milinkovic-Savic t\u1ea1i \u0110T Serbia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU d\u00f9ng Matic th\u0103m d\u00f2 Milinkovic-Savic t\u1ea1i \u0110T Serbia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/mu-muon-mua-milinkovicsavic-va-dung-chieu-doc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Milinkovic-Savic t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i Lazio v\u00e0 Serbia</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMan United trong n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Milinkovic-Savic. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 s\u1eafp chia tay Michael Carrick v\u00e0 Marouane Fellaini do h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. S\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Milinkovic-Savic, r\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p tri\u1ebft l\u00fd c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>D\u00f9ng chi\u00eau \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM.U d\u00f9ng Matic th\u0103m d\u00f2 Milinkovic-Savic l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9c chi\u00eau h\u1ecd m\u1edbi tung ra. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang t\u1eadp trung tr\u00ean \u0110T Serbia d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018. CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n mu\u1ed1n Nemanja Matic ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn \u0111\u00e0n em v\u00e0 khai th\u00e1c d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Lazio.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU muon Matic thuyet phuc Milinkovic-Savic toi Old Trafford\" title=\"MU mu\u1ed1n Matic thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Milinkovic-Savic t\u1edbi Old Trafford\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-206-nho-thuyet-khach-mu-sap-co-bom-tan-100-trieu-euro.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>M.U d\u00f9ng Matic th\u0103m d\u00f2 Milinkovic-Savic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Milinkovic-Savic l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. Anh ch\u01b0a kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i hay n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay v\u1edbi Lazio trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u n\u00f3i quen thu\u1ed9c: \u201cT\u01b0\u01a1ng lai kh\u00f4ng ai \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Milinkovic-Savic v\u1edbi Lazio c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2022. C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Olimpico ngay h\u00e8 n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i r\u00e0o c\u1ea3n l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3. Nh\u01b0 M.U ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n, h\u1ecd t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0a ra \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb l\u00ean t\u1edbi 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng song v\u1eabn b\u1ecb kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb. Lazio nh\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n sao s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 130 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-quyet-chi-166-trieu-bang-cho-nguoi-thay-the-martial-172-189412.html\">MU quy\u1ec7t chi 166 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Martial</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-troi-chan-de-gea-thanh-cong-bang-ban-hop-dong-5-nam-172-188612.html\">M.U tr\u00f3i ch\u00e2n De Gea th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-mu-cong-bo-tan-binh-fred-172-189182.html\">N\u00d3NG: M.U ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh Fred</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/chuyen-toi-man-united-bom-tan-fred-noi-gi-421-189186.html\">Chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Man United, bom t\u1ea5n Fred n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3805","checkdouble":"189490"},{"date":"10:47 25/06","title":"Hazard chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f3 th\u1ea7y m\u1edbi trong 24 gi\u1edd t\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/19/hazard-chuan-bi-co-thay-moi-trong-24-gio-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110ang b\u1eadn chinh chi\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i Nga c\u00f9ng \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia, nh\u01b0ng Hazard chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn tin m\u1eebng v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea7y m\u1edbi. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Chelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Sarri trong th\u1eddi gian s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nConte \u0111i, Sarri \u0111\u1ebfn<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 gi\u00fap The Blues gi\u00e0nh 2 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch trong 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap FA g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, nh\u01b0ng HLV Antonio Conte v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Abramovich \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chia tay chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia t\u1eeb giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, nh\u01b0ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 b\u1ecb ng\u1eebng l\u1ea1i do nh\u1eefng r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 visa, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, Chelsea \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n th\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea3o v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c sa th\u1ea3i Conte, khi h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u1ecf ra to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Juventus c\u01b0\u01a1ng quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ed9 khi c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i n\u00e0y chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, khi The Blues s\u1ebd c\u00f3 thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1edbi trong v\u00f2ng 24 gi\u1edd t\u1edbi &ndash; theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u1eeb b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh. HLV Maurizio Sarri s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea sau nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n t\u00edch c\u1ef1c. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u00f4ng c\u0169ng m\u1edbi b\u1ecb Napoli sa th\u1ea3i, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n t\u1ef1 do l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chia tay Conte, Chelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Sarri thay th\u1ebf\" title=\"Antonio Conte Maurizio Sarri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/30/Eden-Hazard-phat-bieu-ve-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chia tay Conte, Chelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Sarri thay th\u1ebf</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edd Daily Star c\u00f2n cho bi\u1ebft th\u00eam, HLV Sarri y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ed1ng \u1edf khu Cobham, Surrey, g\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea1i b\u1ea3n doanh c\u1ee7a CLB. \u00d4ng s\u1ebd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 2 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Chelsea, c\u00f9ng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u00e9o d\u00e0i th\u00eam 1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u1eefa. 2 b\u00ean s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c k\u00fd k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng trong th\u1eddi gian s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, Sarri c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1eddi huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Chelsea &ndash; Gianfranco Zola gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng tin r\u1ea5t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c, v\u00ec The Blues \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch su\u00f4n s\u1ebb. Nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao nh\u01b0 Hazard hay Courtois c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00f5 t\u00e2n HLV v\u00e0 tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u1edf l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed cho bi\u1ebft s\u1edf d\u0129 Chelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Sarri, b\u1edfi h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch x\u1eed l\u00fd n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Antonio Conte. M\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua, HLV n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111u\u1ed5i Diego Costa qua tin nh\u1eafn, khi\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a anh b\u1ecb s\u1ee5t gi\u1ea3m th\u00ea th\u1ea3m (b\u00e1n cho Atletico v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 58 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-sarri-muon-chelsea-chi-70-trieu-bang-mua-thu-mon-nguoi-brazil-172-189429.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/11/hlv-sarri-muon-chelsea-chi-70-trieu-bang-mua-thu-mon-nguoi-brazil.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-sarri-muon-chelsea-chi-70-trieu-bang-mua-thu-mon-nguoi-brazil-172-189429.html\">HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea chi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil</span><br>\r\nMaurizio Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 Thibaut Courtois ra \u0111i qua \u0111\u00f3 d\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f3n th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-bo-nhiem-sarri-chuong-su-moi-voi-ga-nhan-vien-ngan-hang-172-187380.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/chelsea-bo-nhiem-sarri-thu-thach-long-kien-nhan-voi-ga-nhan-vien-ngan-hang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-bo-nhiem-sarri-chuong-su-moi-voi-ga-nhan-vien-ngan-hang-172-187380.html\">Chelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Sarri: Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1eed m\u1edbi v\u1edbi g\u00e3 nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng</span><br>\r\nChelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Sarri thay th\u1ebf HLV Conte trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao v\u00e0 qua \u0111\u00e2y, Stamford Bridge s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i, k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3804","checkdouble":"189498"},{"date":"11:31 25/06","title":"Luke Shaw khi\u1ebfn Mourinho ph\u00e1t ch\u00e1n khi l\u1ed9 \u201cb\u1ee5ng b\u1ea7u\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/21/luke-shaw-khien-mourinho-phat-chan-khi-lo-bung-bau.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u00e1c C\u0110V Man United \u0111ang ng\u00e1n ng\u1ea9m khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Luke Shaw ph\u00e1t t\u01b0\u1edbng trong k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8.\r\n</h2><h2>Shaw l\u00ean c\u00e2n ch\u00f3ng m\u1eb7t<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110ang \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u1edf Old Trafford, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Luke Shaw ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e0y \u1ea3i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u00ec nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp kh\u00f4ng chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eabn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh trao cho Luke Shaw th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, khi nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111em v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, c\u00f3 th\u00f4ng tin Luke Shaw \u0111ang r\u00e2t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n trong th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i, l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1ea7m. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh &ldquo;ch\u1ed9p&rdquo; \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111ang \u0103n ch\u01a1i &ldquo;ph\u00e8 ph\u1ee1n&rdquo; t\u1ea1i b\u00e3i bi\u1ec3n n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng Ibiza, n\u01a1i v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn trong m\u1ed7i k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, Luke Shaw ph\u00e1t t\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c C\u0110V kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn ra h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"S\u1ed1c v\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh Luke Shaw ph\u00e1t t\u01b0\u1edbng trong k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8\" title=\"S\u1ed1c v\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh Luke Shaw ph\u00e1t t\u01b0\u1edbng trong k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/Soc-voi-hinh-anh-Luke-Shaw-phat-tuong-trong-ky-nghi-he-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Luke Shaw ph\u00e1t t\u01b0\u1edbng trong k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nV\u1edbi th\u00e2n h\u00ecnh &ldquo;c\u1ed3ng k\u1ec1nh&rdquo; nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Man United, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u khi Jose Mourinho v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Asley Young &ndash; m\u1ed9t &ldquo;\u00f4ng gi\u00e0&rdquo; 32 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh, khi th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2014, nh\u01b0ng Luke Shaw ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi y\u00eau qu\u00fd m\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. T\u1eebng l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 1 x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9, gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y Shaw ph\u1ea3i theo d\u00f5i \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1 World Cup, trong t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng v\u00e1c &ldquo;b\u1ee5ng b\u1ea7u&rdquo;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi c\u00f2n 2 th\u00e1ng n\u1eefa s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra, v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh Luke Shaw ph\u00e1t t\u01b0\u1edbng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n, g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec3 anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-bi-chi-trich-vi-cach-doi-xu-voi-3-cau-thu-mu-172-186875.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/20/mourinho-bi-chi-trich-vi-cach-doi-xu-voi-3-cau-thu-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-bi-chi-trich-vi-cach-doi-xu-voi-3-cau-thu-mu-172-186875.html\">Mourinho b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00ec c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed v\u1edbi 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 MU</span><br />\r\nHuy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Ian Wright l\u00ean \u00e1n HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha sau nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 \u0111ang l\u00e0m v\u1edbi Marcus Rashford, Paul Pogba v\u00e0 Luke Shaw.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-nhin-mu-chieu-mo-diogo-dalot-172-187924.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/7/goc-nhin-mu-chieu-mo-diogo-dalot.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-nhin-mu-chieu-mo-diogo-dalot-172-187924.html\">G\u00f3c M.U: 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Diogo Dalot l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f3n h\u1eddi!</span><br />\r\nT\u1ed1i qua (6/6), th\u00f4ng tin ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1: MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Diogo Dalot t\u1eeb Porto. Nh\u01b0 l\u1eddi HLV Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh hay nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3803","checkdouble":"189507"}]}